docs.abstract: The e-commerce giant, while mulling 20 finalists for its second headquarters, has kept up a “blistering” pace of expansion for technology jobs and fulfillment centers.
docs.snippet: The e-commerce giant, while mulling 20 finalists for its second headquarters, has kept up a “blistering” pace of expansion for technology jobs and fulfillment centers.
docs.lead_paragraph: As Amazon dances through courtship rituals with the 20 cities hoping to host its second headquarters, the company is also charging ahead on a slate of other real estate projects.

headline.main: Amazon, Not Waiting for HQ2, Announces Projects in Boston and Vancouver
headline.print_headline: Amazon Projects on ‘Blistering Pace’ As Cities Await Word on New Campus

docs.abstract: He could double the National Cancer Institute’s budget or tutor two million students in math every year for all time.
docs.snippet: He could double the National Cancer Institute’s budget or tutor two million students in math every year for all time.
docs.lead_paragraph: CHICAGO — Jeff Bezos, the founder of Amazon, is one of the most successful businessmen of all time. He has amassed an unfathomable fortune, reportedly $131 billion. This presents a predicament. Mr. Bezos commands far more money than any one person could possibly spend, far more than any one family dynasty could possibly spend. What should he do with all this money?

headline.main: Better Ways for Jeff Bezos to Spend $131 Billion

docs.abstract: Unrestrained strongmen use the state to punish — or silence — their enemies.
docs.snippet: Unrestrained strongmen use the state to punish — or silence — their enemies.
docs.lead_paragraph: President Trump has declared war on Amazon, the nation’s second most valuable company. Amazon is creating more jobs than all but a handful of entire states. And nearly every major city in the country is vying to land the second headquarters of this global retailer and the 50,000 high-paying positions it promises to bring.

headline.main: America Last: Trump’s Attack on the Amazon Job Machine
headline.print_headline: America Last: Trump’s Attack on the Amazon Job Machine
